rds similar armor.<br><br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/equipment/veliousarmour.html">Velious: The Frozen Isle</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br>The continent of Velious opened up all new options for warriors. Three factions exist on the icy landmass, and each has its advantages.<br><br>The Coldain provide the invaluable ring quests, which return an extraordinary piece of jewelry.<br><br>The Dragon Kin give one of the better suits of armor, as do the giants of Kael Drakkel.<br><br>To find more information on these suits, try this link.<br><br>There is also the single quest who’s very roots sink deep into the history of Norrath, stretching back into the rivers of time to give us adventurers a glimpse of the old world as it once was, and to prove our greatness to our fellow adventurers.<br><br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/qsearch.html?zone=70">The Plane of Sky</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br>The Plane of Sky, home to the great Crystalline dragon, is a great undertaking for any warrior. Within are housed great prizes for any warrior... if they can prove themselves worthy.<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/qsearch.html?zone=116">Allakhazam's Temple of Veeshan Quests</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.phantomraiders.com/open/tears.htm">Halls of Testing Quest Spread</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br>The Temple of Veeshan opens up a whole new world of power high-end items to a warrior. Here, a warrior can face some of the greatest perils ever, and should he prevail, prove his worth in the eyes of dragonkind.<br><br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.steelwarrior.org/epic.html">Epic Quest: The Jagged Blade of War Checklist</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=768">Allakhazam's Warrior Epic Walkthrough</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br>These quests are profound journeys that stretch across the entire multiverse of Norrath. It is these quests which are the major achievement of a warrior’s career, for while the reward may be surpassed, the prestige is gargantuan.<br><br>The warrior epic quest is the history of an ancient blade forged by the God of War, Rallos Zek. A complete checklist of all the steps can be found in the Questin’ section of the Steel Warrior board. At the present time, all known steps that require two items can be multi-quested. Please inform me if for some reason one of these steps does not, in fact, work.<br><br>Should you come across an item in your travels that you seem to think would serve some greater purpose, but aren't sure or can't find to find any information about it, various information about quest items can be found at...<br><br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://home.carolina.rr.com/bluescreen/items/items.htm">Quest Items Discovery Page</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br><br><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i>     Note: If anyone desires to see something else up here, has a link they think should be added, or a question they would like to have posted here, please email me at</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <!--EZCODE MAIL START--><a href="mailto: talic@steelwarrior.org"> talic@steelwarrior.org</a><!--EZCODE MAIL END--><br> <p><img src=http://www.warghoul.com/images/talicsig.jpg ></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utalicmoore.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talic Moore</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://forums.interealms.com/ranger/images/icons/Yin_Yang.gif" BORDER=0> at: 4/4/02 5:04:34 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=376.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarrio